=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex6 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright mixed sound, with complex oscillator character around 52 Hz, featuring punchy attack and impulsive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with highpass character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: impulsive
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: highpass
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 52.3647
  harmonic_decay_rate: -4.8878
  harmonic_regularity: 0.4672
  pitch_clarity: 0.8803
  inharmonicity: 0.0411
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: 7.1010
  resonance_freq: 1033.5938

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
